Gnucash for Android (gnc4a) Project Overview
============================================

-----------------
Files and Folders
-----------------

COPYING				- GPL v3 Agreement
HACKING  			- Conventions used, basic devel orientation
OVERVIEW  			- This file 
project/gnc4android		- Project root directory
   AndroidManifest.xml		- Program android manifest
   assets			- (currently empty)
   bin				- compiled programs, scripts
   default.properties		- Auto-generated properties file (don't touch)
   gen				- Auto-generated resource files (don't touch)
   res				- Android resource XML files (UI layout, etc...)
   src/				- Source files- root directory
   test/			- Test project files

------------------------
Source File Descriptions
------------------------

AccountsActivity.java    	- Action Listener/Event Handler for UI
AccountSpinnerData.java  	- Account Spinner class- creates account list and interprets account types
BookDetailsActivity.java  	- This class displays opened Book details
GNCAndroid.java           	- Main program class
GNCDataHandler.java		- Data Handling/SQL interfacing classes
FileChooser.java		- Class for choosing accounts file
MainView.java			- Main UI class- calls subactivities
Preferences.java		- Displays and edits user preferences
QuickEntryActivity.java		- Quick entry transaction class


